{"tid":475687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不法癖好】涉藏兒童色情物品 《浪客劍心》作者認喜歡兒童裸體","createTime":"2017-11-21T10:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T14:17:16.000Z","uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a195e7823deeaecbd21c30745433f7d6d07dfc2d","tid":475687,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:46:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171121&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57485665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171121%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57485665&d=I3169T1L%2FPFmetaPytazgRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=4264789e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171121%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57485665&h=6c7f6f2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171121&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57485665</a><br />\n日本人氣漫畫《浪客劍心》的作者和月伸宏（真名：西脇伸宏），涉嫌違反《禁止兒童買春和兒童色情法》，周二被警視廳送檢。西脇承認犯案並直言喜歡兒童裸體。<br />\n<br />\n47歲的西脇伸宏已婚，太太是小説家黑碕薫。案情指西脇在今年10月，於位於東京都是辦公室內，藏有多隻拍攝10至15歲女孩裸體的DVD。警方是在調查另一宗兒童色情物品案件時發現西脇涉案，遂派員到他住所及辦公室搜查。西脇承認犯案，他說：「喜歡兒童裸體，買入了DVD及靜止畫像。」西脇又透露，自己偏好「小學高年級生至中學二年級左右的女孩」。<br />\n<br />\n日本是在近年修改法律，凡為滿足性好奇心而持有兒童色情物品的人，亦成為處罰對象，面臨1年以下監禁或100萬日圓（約6.94萬港元）以下罰款。<br />\n<br />\n日本《朝日新聞》/《讀賣新聞》"},{"pid":"1792799ff2bf7d3f6a6d9bacb3e696793be168d1","tid":475687,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-21T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171121&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=57485665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171121%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57485665&d=I3169T1L%2FPFmetaPytazgRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=4264789e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171121%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D57485665&h=6c7f6f2e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171121&amp;s=10793140&amp;a